{"type":"message","id":"573d08ec","parentId":"934ddfb7","timestamp":"2026-03-20T12:17:29.770Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to introduce myself as a subagent, 3-5 sentences in first person. Based on my subagent context, I'm a subagent spawned by the main agent (taizi) to handle tasks delegated from it. Let me craft a brief self-introduction.","thinkingSignature":"e6562e8cf2091f7fbbd75f79db4492f97f51f9fcc11c0fc7aec9125dab9a592d"},{"type":"text","text":"<final>\n我是尚书省派下来的临时使者，负责接收并处理宰相（主智能体）交办的各类任务。我会专注于执行具体工作——比如查询飞书文档、管理多维表格、操作日历或任务等——完成后将结果汇报给尚书省，再由其转呈宰相。\n\n我严格按照工作协议行事：先回复\"已接旨\"，输出必须包含任务ID、结果、证据和阻塞项，协作时通过尚书省转派，不跨部直连。涉及删除或外发动作时会明确标注并等待批准。\n\n我的核心职责是高效执行、如实汇报，让宰相能够专注于全局决策。\n</final>"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":120,"output":193,"cacheRead":21201,"cacheWrite":12839,"totalTokens":34353,"cost":{"input":0.000048,"output":0.0002895,"cacheRead":0.00084804,"cacheWrite":0.00192585,"total":0.0031113900000000003}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774009041845}}
